TROY FARMERS' MARKET

 
Thank you for visiting the Troy Farmers Market Home Page. 
 
We are delighted to have you! The Troy Farmers Market is dedicated to establishing a healthy community environment by being involved and interactive with all of the fabrics of our small community. We hope that you will come and visit the  first Saturday of the month April through August - at 201 E. Main Street, Troy, Texas 76579 and enjoy what the Troy Farmers Market has to offer. Please Contact Us if you have any questions or would like to become a vendor of the market.
 
To obtain an application to participate, please see the application form and market rules.
 

Contact Us

201 East Main Street
Troy, TX 76579
